column5: If theres such a thing as a turducken.....what do you call this a muskass???    http://www.lindnermedia.com/angling-edge/video/fish-lifetime

Wow that's cool...funny thing i've heard of these things happening and this past weekend i actually had a similar experience. I had a smallie on and the musky took a couple runs at it but never ate it? Gave me and my daughter a thrill to see it happen tho
had that happen a bunch of times...  had a musky grab a 25 inch walleye this summer...
Big fish. Wonder if it swam away....

Yes...lol this has happened to me as well...reeling up a bass and then the famous V and thump and now your fighting a muskie.....although my muskies have never totally swallowed the bass so only the bass was hooked......and its awesome when they hit up close ...little freaky even.
Very cool video! I've never had it happen to me... but would love to experience that! Especially if you get to land the ski!
